    <h1>About ProjektVPN</h1>
    <p>
      ProjektVPN is a VPN server hosting system designed to be deployed anonymously. All payments are made in <a href="https://bitcoin.org/">Bitcoin</a> and all traffic is routed over <a href="https://github.com/cjdelisle/cjdns#cjdns">a secure mesh network</a>.
    </p>
